&lt;p&gt;As a Representative for the Concierge team, you&#39;ll be the company&#39;s voice and will use exceptional empathy and product expertise to ensure our users feel understood and valued. Your mission will be to solve customer issues efficiently and effectively, while proactively connecting with them throughout the day.&lt;/p&gt;
